title: Engineering Vibrations 4e - Inman
description:
This is the 4th edition E-book of engineering vibration by Daniel Inman alongside both the ebook and solutions manual for the 3rd edition. I couldn't find these anywhere else so I figured I might as well upload them here. Hopefully the 3rd has enough solved examples to help you learn how to solve anything in the new one. Good luck and happy studying future engineers!
